OL,3,CSeven children and a man drown in
OL,4,Cincidents over Bank Holiday weekend
OL,6,FSeven children and one man have
OL,7,Fdrowned in separate open water
OL,8,Fincidents over the Bank Holiday
OL,9,Fweekend amid record-breaking
OL,10,Ftemperatures across the UK.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, the body of a teenage
OL,13,Fboy was recovered from Hawley Lake
OL,14,Fnear Blackwater, in Hampshire.
OL,16,FThe boy was first reported missing on
OL,17,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
