OL,3,CSeven children and a man drown in
OL,4,Cincidents over Bank Holiday weekend
OL,6,FWhile formal identification has not
OL,7,Fyet taken place, Hampshire and Isle of
OL,8,FWight Police say the family of the
OL,9,Fmissing boy have been notified.
OL,11,FSo far, those reported to have died in
OL,12,Fwater incidents are:
OL,14,FAlso on Wednesday, a body was found
OL,15,Fduring the search for a 17-year-old
OL,16,Fboy last seen at a lake in Cheshire.
OL,18,FA Cheshire Constabulary spokesperson
OL,19,Fsaid officers were called to reports
OL,20,Fof a missing boy last seen in the
OL,21,Fwater at Pickmere Lake, near Northwich.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
