OL,3,CSeven children and a man drown in
OL,4,Cincidents over Bank Holiday weekend
OL,6,FAfter finding the body of the 17-year-
OL,7,Fold, Chief Inspector Jamie Lewis said:
OL,8,F"This was a young boy who had his
OL,9,Fentire life ahead of him. At what is
OL,10,Fan incredibly difficult time, our
OL,11,Fthoughts remain with the boy's family,
OL,12,Ffriends and everyone who knew him."
OL,14,FThree teenage boys and one girl also
OL,15,Fdied in separate incidents over the
OL,16,FBank Holiday weekend after going into
OL,17,Fthe water in Lincolnshire, South
OL,18,FYorkshire, West Yorkshire, and
OL,19,FWarwickshire.
