OL,3,CSeven children and a man drown in
OL,4,Cincidents over Bank Holiday weekend
OL,6,FReco Puttock, 13, was pronounced dead
OL,7,Fin hospital after he was pulled from a
OL,8,Freservoir at Leadbeater Dam, Halifax,
OL,9,Fjust after 3pm on Monday, West
OL,10,FYorkshire Police said.
OL,12,FCalderdale CID is investigating the
OL,13,Fdeath, but it is not believed to be
OL,14,Fsuspicious.
OL,16,FPaying tribute to Reco, King Cross
OL,17,FPark Rugby League Club, in Halifax,
OL,18,Fsaid: "There are no words we can say
OL,19,Fwhich will make this loss any less
OL,20,Fpainful for his family and friends
OL,21,Fespecially at such a young age.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
