OL,3,CSeven children and a man drown in
OL,4,Cincidents over Bank Holiday weekend
OL,6,F"So, on behalf of the entire club, we
OL,7,Fwould like to extend our thoughts and
OL,8,Fcondolences with his family, friends
OL,9,Fand team mates."
OL,11,FHours later, the body of a teenage
OL,12,Fgirl was recovered from Kingsbury
OL,13,FWater Park, just south of Tamworth,
OL,14,FStaffordshire, on Monday evening
OL,15,Ffollowing a police search.
OL,17,FDespite the efforts of emergency
OL,18,Fservices, she was pronounced dead at
OL,19,Fthe scene, Atherstone and Coleshill
OL,20,FPolice said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
