OL,3,CSeven children and a man drown in
OL,4,Cincidents over Bank Holiday weekend
OL,6,FThe body of another boy was found at
OL,7,FRother Valley Country Park during the
OL,8,Fearly hours of Tuesday morning,
OL,9,Ffollowing reports of a missing child
OL,10,Fseen entering the water but not
OL,11,Fgetting out.
OL,13,FSouth Yorkshire Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService and the Yorkshire Ambulance
OL,15,FService had launched a specialist
OL,16,Fsearch operation shortly before 7pm on
OL,17,FMonday.
OL,19,FFormal identification has not been
OL,20,Fconfirmed, but the boy's family has
OL,21,Fbeen informed, police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
