OL,3,CSeven children and a man drown in
OL,4,Cincidents over Bank Holiday weekend
OL,6,FThe incidents follow the death of 15-
OL,7,Fyear-old Declan Sawyer, whose body was
OL,8,Ffound in a Lincoln lake on Sunday
OL,9,Faround 10.25pm.
OL,11,FDeclan's father Carl described him as
OL,12,F"a funny and outgoing young man who
OL,13,Floved fishing and football," as he
OL,14,Fcalled on families to take care of
OL,15,Ftheir children when near water.
OL,17,F"He had a very cheeky smile and the
OL,18,Fpersonality to match. He was very much
OL,19,Floved by his friends and family, and
OL,20,Fwill be missed dearly by many," Carl
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
