OL,3,CSeven children and a man drown in
OL,4,Cincidents over Bank Holiday weekend
OL,6,F"Please can all parents, friends and
OL,7,Ffamily make their children aware of
OL,8,Fthe dangers surrounding water."
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FA man in his 60s also died at Tregirls
OL,16,FBeach, near Padstow, on Monday after
OL,17,Fsuffering a cardiac arrest in the sea
OL,18,Fwhile trying to help family members
OL,19,Fwho had got into difficulty in the
OL,20,Fwater, Devon and Cornwall Police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
