OL,3,CSeven children and a man drown in
OL,4,Cincidents over Bank Holiday weekend
OL,6,FThe relatives were brought to shore by
OL,7,Fmembers of the public during the
OL,8,Fincident.
OL,10,FOn Wednesday, police in Hampshire said
OL,11,Fofficers were searching for a missing
OL,12,Fteenager who was reportedly last seen
OL,13,Fswimming at a lake near Blackwater.
OL,15,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Police
OL,16,Fsaid a multi-agency operation is
OL,17,Funderway at Hawley Lake to find the
OL,18,Fboy, who was first reported missing at
OL,19,F3:28pm on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
