OL,3,CSeven children and a man drown in
OL,4,Cincidents over Bank Holiday weekend
OL,6,FThe Met Office said Tuesday was the
OL,7,FUK's hottest day in May on record,
OL,8,Fbreaking records set the previous two
OL,9,Fdays.
OL,11,FTemperatures provisionally reached 35C
OL,12,Fat Heathrow and Kew Gardens in London,
OL,13,Fwhile Cardiff Bute Park recorded 32.9C.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
